13
00:01:41,000 --> 00:01:43,980
=Episode 36=

14
00:01:44,400 --> 00:01:45,870
In this world, many parents

15
00:01:46,510 --> 00:01:49,710
seem to always consider
and plan for their children.

16
00:01:49,840 --> 00:01:50,920
But in fact,

17
00:01:51,400 --> 00:01:53,590
they do not really care
about their children's feelings.

18
00:01:54,590 --> 00:01:56,790
They can even sacrifice their children's

19
00:01:57,510 --> 00:01:58,480
reputation and dignity

20
00:01:58,480 --> 00:02:00,070
for their own interests.

21
00:02:01,150 --> 00:02:02,230
Most of the time,

22
00:02:03,230 --> 00:02:05,070
the children are also helpless.

23
00:02:07,150 --> 00:02:08,240
As a woman,

24
00:02:09,000 --> 00:02:10,560
I understand well how much discipline

25
00:02:11,000 --> 00:02:12,910
Cousin Lian has endured since childhood.

26
00:02:14,800 --> 00:02:16,310
If I had such a mother,

27
00:02:16,960 --> 00:02:18,590
I wouldn't do better than her.

28
00:02:18,960 --> 00:02:20,030
I understand what you mean.

29
00:02:20,450 --> 00:02:21,840
I will go talk to her and make it clear.

30
00:02:26,150 --> 00:02:26,990
Sister,

31
00:02:27,710 --> 00:02:29,150
I have treated you well

32
00:02:29,560 --> 00:02:31,000
over the years,

33
00:02:31,560 --> 00:02:33,960
yet today you still came
to the mansion to force me.

34
00:02:34,150 --> 00:02:35,520
Do you really think

35
00:02:35,630 --> 00:02:36,840
I'm that foolish?

36
00:02:42,030 --> 00:02:44,630
Sister, you hold a high position
in the Lord's Mansion.

37
00:02:48,680 --> 00:02:50,000
I deserve to be

38
00:02:50,800 --> 00:02:52,190
treated well by you.

39
00:02:55,750 --> 00:02:56,680
Have you forgotten

40
00:02:58,400 --> 00:02:59,680
that the Consort Dowager

41
00:02:59,680 --> 00:03:01,240
should not have been you?

42
00:03:02,630 --> 00:03:03,560
If I didn't give

43
00:03:03,680 --> 00:03:05,030
the marriage opportunity to you

44
00:03:05,080 --> 00:03:06,630
and married into the Lian family,

45
00:03:08,280 --> 00:03:09,960
it would have been you,

46
00:03:10,680 --> 00:03:12,310
living under others' thumb

47
00:03:12,310 --> 00:03:14,430
for so many years.

48
00:03:19,840 --> 00:03:21,150
The title of Consort Dowager.

49
00:03:21,240 --> 00:03:22,590
The glory and wealth.

50
00:03:26,030 --> 00:03:27,310
Those are what you owe me.

51
00:03:29,000 --> 00:03:30,710
You must compensate me for a lifetime!

52
00:03:33,910 --> 00:03:35,590
Xingzhou says I shows partiality to you.

53
00:03:36,680 --> 00:03:37,590
He doesn't know

54
00:03:37,680 --> 00:03:38,800
that my greatest partiality

55
00:03:39,190 --> 00:03:40,910
is always treating you sincerely,

56
00:03:40,960 --> 00:03:42,520
even when I know that you are insincere,

57
00:03:43,240 --> 00:03:45,470
everytime you call me sister.

58
00:03:47,430 --> 00:03:49,240
Listen to me carefully.

59
00:03:49,910 --> 00:03:51,030
My title

60
00:03:51,680 --> 00:03:53,030
was not given by you.

61
00:03:54,000 --> 00:03:56,080
It was you who made the wrong choice
and regretted it.

62
00:03:56,680 --> 00:03:57,520
My family

63
00:03:58,560 --> 00:03:59,750
never owed you anything.

64
00:04:01,190 --> 00:04:02,030
Sister.

65
00:04:02,080 --> 00:04:03,430
Sister, sister, sister.

66
00:04:03,840 --> 00:04:04,680
I'm begging you.

67
00:04:04,710 --> 00:04:06,430
Help me one last time.

68
00:04:07,430 --> 00:04:08,270
Her...

69
00:04:08,800 --> 00:04:10,680
Her reputation is all ruined.

70
00:04:10,870 --> 00:04:12,870
No one wants her now.

71
00:04:14,840 --> 00:04:15,680
Right.

72
00:04:16,040 --> 00:04:16,880
Right.

73
00:04:16,890 --> 00:04:17,830
I will beg Princess Huaisang.

74
00:04:17,920 --> 00:04:18,920
I will apologize to her.

75
00:04:19,160 --> 00:04:20,360
If she is really willing-

76
00:04:20,480 --> 00:04:21,800
- I will-
- I won't agree either.

77
00:04:22,830 --> 00:04:23,830
My daughter-in-law

78
00:04:23,950 --> 00:04:25,800
is a one-in-a-million good girl.

79
00:04:26,390 --> 00:04:27,560
Let me make it clear.

80
00:04:28,240 --> 00:04:29,080
From now on,

81
00:04:29,190 --> 00:04:30,720
if anyone dares

82
00:04:30,920 --> 00:04:33,000
to force my son to have any concubines

83
00:04:33,560 --> 00:04:35,270
and upset my daughter-in-law,

84
00:04:36,310 --> 00:04:38,000
I will be the first to make them pay.

85
00:04:39,560 --> 00:04:40,510
Sister.

86
00:04:41,390 --> 00:04:42,390
Sister.

87
00:04:42,430 --> 00:04:43,720
Sister, sister!

88
00:04:44,190 --> 00:04:47,040
Please help me one last time!

89
00:04:47,270 --> 00:04:50,160
Please help Binglan one last time!

90
00:04:50,240 --> 00:04:52,720
I'm begging you.

91
00:05:16,510 --> 00:05:17,350
Binglan.

92
00:05:23,560 --> 00:05:24,400
Look.

93
00:05:26,800 --> 00:05:28,830
The lights of the mansion
are so beautiful.

94
00:05:30,430 --> 00:05:31,630
Since I was a kid,

95
00:05:32,120 --> 00:05:33,120
in my heart,

96
00:05:34,390 --> 00:05:35,750
nothing outside

97
00:05:35,870 --> 00:05:37,630
can compare to what this mansion has.

98
00:05:40,510 --> 00:05:41,600
And no one...

99
00:05:52,480 --> 00:05:53,430
And no one

100
00:05:54,430 --> 00:05:56,000
can compare to you.

101
00:06:01,480 --> 00:06:02,800
I have always

102
00:06:02,920 --> 00:06:04,390
owed you an apology.

103
00:06:06,070 --> 00:06:07,000
At the beginning,

104
00:06:07,070 --> 00:06:09,120
when I didn't even understand
what marriage meant,

105
00:06:10,000 --> 00:06:11,160
I let Mother

106
00:06:11,920 --> 00:06:13,360
arrange this marriage.

107
00:06:13,800 --> 00:06:14,640
For you,

108
00:06:15,430 --> 00:06:16,830
it was indeed a great injustice.

109
00:06:19,800 --> 00:06:20,750
I was also at fault.

110
00:06:23,310 --> 00:06:24,430
I have long known

111
00:06:25,190 --> 00:06:26,270
that you had

112
00:06:26,950 --> 00:06:28,430
no feelings for me.

113
00:06:29,950 --> 00:06:32,310
I had already given up
on winning your love.

114
00:06:33,920 --> 00:06:35,190
But all these years,

115
00:06:36,360 --> 00:06:38,000
I kept telling myself

116
00:06:38,800 --> 00:06:39,800
that love is useless

117
00:06:40,600 --> 00:06:42,310
and as long I became Princess Huaiyang,

118
00:06:42,600 --> 00:06:45,270
I could get everything I ever dreamed of.

119
00:06:47,510 --> 00:06:48,560
But today,

120
00:06:50,160 --> 00:06:51,600
when you stood up

121
00:06:51,950 --> 00:06:54,040
in front of Princess Huaisang,
I finally realized

122
00:06:55,240 --> 00:06:57,430
that all these years, I didn't get

123
00:06:58,070 --> 00:07:00,360
what I fought so hard for.
Instead, I lost it all.

124
00:07:02,560 --> 00:07:03,800
I lost you.

125
00:07:05,870 --> 00:07:07,800
I lost my dignity

126
00:07:09,240 --> 00:07:10,270
and my grace.

127
00:07:12,430 --> 00:07:14,600
I even lost myself.

128
00:07:36,510 --> 00:07:37,360
It's okay.

129
00:07:38,390 --> 00:07:39,390
I'm fine now.

130
00:07:40,800 --> 00:07:41,800
It's cold late at night.

131
00:07:43,120 --> 00:07:44,510
Cousin, please go back.

132
00:07:48,680 --> 00:07:49,520
Binglan.

133
00:07:51,720 --> 00:07:53,000
There's still time.

134
00:07:54,750 --> 00:07:55,590
I believe in you.

135
00:08:07,120 --> 00:08:09,000
Binglan, Binglan. Wait!

136
00:08:09,190 --> 00:08:10,030
Binglan!

137
00:08:10,920 --> 00:08:12,480
If it weren't for your incompetence,

138
00:08:12,920 --> 00:08:14,630
I would have helped you
to be the concubine.

139
00:08:14,870 --> 00:08:16,680
I don't want to be a concubine anymore.

140
00:08:19,480 --> 00:08:20,320
Mother,

141
00:08:20,680 --> 00:08:21,950
have you ever thought about it?

142
00:08:22,360 --> 00:08:24,360
The Lord Huaiyang doesn't love me.

143
00:08:25,190 --> 00:08:26,720
Even if I marry into the family,

144
00:08:27,240 --> 00:08:29,270
what kind of life will I live?

145
00:08:29,630 --> 00:08:31,600
Are you foolish?

146
00:08:32,200 --> 00:08:33,270
Once you marry him,

147
00:08:33,320 --> 00:08:35,270
none of this will matter.

148
00:08:36,150 --> 00:08:37,870
Have you forgotten what I planned

149
00:08:38,480 --> 00:08:39,790
and everything I did for you

150
00:08:39,790 --> 00:08:40,960
all these years?

151
00:08:41,590 --> 00:08:42,630
Is it for me,

152
00:08:44,000 --> 00:08:45,240
or for yourself?

153
00:08:48,840 --> 00:08:49,870
From now on,

154
00:08:50,480 --> 00:08:51,870
I will no longer live

155
00:08:51,870 --> 00:08:53,440
for your illusory dreams.

156
00:08:54,840 --> 00:08:56,120
My marriage

157
00:08:56,550 --> 00:08:57,630
and my life

158
00:08:58,080 --> 00:08:59,750
will be decided by myself.

159
00:09:01,480 --> 00:09:02,320
Binglan.

160
00:09:06,670 --> 00:09:07,750
Binglan.

161
00:09:14,600 --> 00:09:15,870
Binglan.

162
00:09:34,320 --> 00:09:35,320
Now,

163
00:09:36,270 --> 00:09:37,670
we have no more worries.

164
00:09:39,080 --> 00:09:40,150
Are you happy?

165
00:09:40,870 --> 00:09:42,630
You have prepared everything,

166
00:09:42,960 --> 00:09:44,720
so I don't have to worry at all.

167
00:09:45,480 --> 00:09:46,550
There were some surprises,

168
00:09:47,440 --> 00:09:49,000
but there was also joy.

169
00:09:50,320 --> 00:09:52,870
Sounds like you have some complaints?

170
00:09:53,670 --> 00:09:54,510
Yes.

171
00:09:56,270 --> 00:09:58,630
We have gone through so many
twists and turns,

172
00:09:58,670 --> 00:09:59,870
before today.

173
00:10:00,670 --> 00:10:01,510
Perhaps,

174
00:10:01,960 --> 00:10:03,790
if we had a deeper connection of fate,

175
00:10:04,030 --> 00:10:04,870
and met earlier,

176
00:10:05,550 --> 00:10:07,630
our path would have been easier.

177
00:10:08,510 --> 00:10:09,350
In the past,

178
00:10:10,030 --> 00:10:11,600
I did have such complaints.

179
00:10:11,910 --> 00:10:12,870
And now?

180
00:10:13,150 --> 00:10:14,960
Now, I am very grateful for all of this.

181
00:10:16,790 --> 00:10:18,030
It is hard-earned,

182
00:10:19,000 --> 00:10:19,960
so

183
00:10:21,080 --> 00:10:22,510
I will cherish it even more.

184
00:10:27,240 --> 00:10:28,080
I have

185
00:10:29,840 --> 00:10:31,150
proposed to you many times,

186
00:10:32,870 --> 00:10:34,120
but I felt it wasn't enough.

187
00:10:37,000 --> 00:10:37,840
Today,

188
00:10:39,270 --> 00:10:40,510
I sincerely ask again

189
00:10:41,200 --> 00:10:42,550
to take you as my wife.

190
00:10:48,150 --> 00:10:49,030
From now on,

191
00:10:49,630 --> 00:10:50,670
we'll care for each other,

192
00:10:51,030 --> 00:10:52,200
and live in harmony.

193
00:10:55,480 --> 00:10:56,790
Will you marry me?

194
00:10:58,240 --> 00:10:59,600
Yes, with all my heart.

195
00:11:06,360 --> 00:11:07,630
Since you said yes,

196
00:11:09,000 --> 00:11:11,270
let me tell you another secret.

197
00:11:12,440 --> 00:11:13,320
On the 9th,

198
00:11:14,390 --> 00:11:15,360
we will have our wedding.

199
00:11:16,000 --> 00:11:16,960
The 9th?

200
00:11:17,720 --> 00:11:18,960
It's just a few days away.

201
00:11:19,000 --> 00:11:19,960
Will we make it?

202
00:11:20,960 --> 00:11:22,200
All the friends and family

203
00:11:22,600 --> 00:11:23,870
have already been notified.

204
00:11:24,630 --> 00:11:25,720
Even if we hold it tomorrow,

205
00:11:26,000 --> 00:11:26,840
we'll make it.

206
00:11:27,030 --> 00:11:28,200
You are in such a hurry.

207
00:11:28,270 --> 00:11:29,270
You fear I'll run away?

208
00:11:29,270 --> 00:11:30,110
Yes.

209
00:11:33,200 --> 00:11:34,150
During this journey,

210
00:11:34,600 --> 00:11:36,270
we've wandered around and come this far.

211
00:11:36,840 --> 00:11:37,790
It hasn't been easy.

212
00:11:39,150 --> 00:11:40,320
We've weathered many storms.

213
00:11:41,870 --> 00:11:43,000
I can't wait any longer.

214
00:11:44,030 --> 00:11:44,870
In the future,

215
00:11:45,270 --> 00:11:46,510
no matter how hard it gets,

216
00:11:47,390 --> 00:11:48,750
I will protect you from any harm.

217
00:11:50,120 --> 00:11:50,960
I only wish to

218
00:11:51,910 --> 00:11:52,750
hold your hand,

219
00:11:54,440 --> 00:11:55,480
and grow old together.

220
00:12:05,940 --> 00:12:10,010
(Fanglan Pavilion)

221
00:12:10,010 --> 00:12:10,850
- Okay.
- It's good?

222
00:12:11,640 --> 00:12:12,480
It's fine. It's fine.

223
00:12:13,750 --> 00:12:14,790
Take it slow.

224
00:12:15,390 --> 00:12:16,230
Dear,

225
00:12:16,750 --> 00:12:17,590
pass it to me again.

226
00:12:18,750 --> 00:12:19,600
Take it slow.

227
00:12:20,200 --> 00:12:21,040
Look.

228
00:12:26,200 --> 00:12:27,750
So majestic!

229
00:12:29,870 --> 00:12:30,710
Wow.

230
00:12:32,120 --> 00:12:34,240
Princess Huaisang has this much dowry?

231
00:12:37,270 --> 00:12:38,390
It's really a lot.

232
00:12:43,510 --> 00:12:44,350
Miantang.

233
00:12:45,240 --> 00:12:46,080
Miantang.

234
00:12:46,200 --> 00:12:47,480
- Darling.
- Grandfather.

235
00:12:50,360 --> 00:12:51,200
Grandfather.

236
00:12:54,150 --> 00:12:54,990
Uncle.

237
00:12:55,120 --> 00:12:55,960
Miantang.

238
00:12:56,910 --> 00:12:57,750
Miantang.

239
00:12:59,790 --> 00:13:00,670
Let me see.

240
00:13:02,150 --> 00:13:03,390
Lord Cui

241
00:13:03,440 --> 00:13:04,840
has made you so thin!

242
00:13:04,960 --> 00:13:05,840
Really?

243
00:13:07,000 --> 00:13:07,840
Yes.

244
00:13:08,080 --> 00:13:09,720
I heard this place
has been chaotic lately.

245
00:13:10,000 --> 00:13:10,910
Are you alright?

246
00:13:11,360 --> 00:13:12,720
Right, is there anyone

247
00:13:12,840 --> 00:13:14,080
bullying you in the mansion?

248
00:13:14,600 --> 00:13:15,720
You keep asking questions.

249
00:13:15,840 --> 00:13:17,030
I don't know how to answer.

250
00:13:17,120 --> 00:13:18,390
My tongue is feeling numb.

251
00:13:19,200 --> 00:13:20,040
Grandfather,

252
00:13:20,080 --> 00:13:21,480
please go inside and have some tea.

253
00:13:21,510 --> 00:13:23,000
I'll take you to the mansion to meet

254
00:13:23,150 --> 00:13:24,320
the Lord and his mother later.

255
00:13:24,390 --> 00:13:25,270
No, that's not allowed.

256
00:13:25,670 --> 00:13:26,510
It's not allowed.

257
00:13:26,550 --> 00:13:27,750
An unmarried girl cannot

258
00:13:27,840 --> 00:13:29,030
meet her future husband.

259
00:13:29,030 --> 00:13:30,200
It's against the rules.

260
00:13:30,360 --> 00:13:31,200
Let's go. Let's go.

261
00:13:33,550 --> 00:13:35,270
- You're getting more lovely.
- Please.

262
00:13:47,030 --> 00:13:47,870
Father.

263
00:13:49,600 --> 00:13:50,440
Brother.

264
00:13:53,150 --> 00:13:53,990
Father.

265
00:13:56,120 --> 00:13:56,960
Here.

266
00:14:02,440 --> 00:14:03,600
Father, take a look.

267
00:14:03,670 --> 00:14:04,790
Any other suggestions?

268
