(Joy)

269
00:14:15,630 --> 00:14:16,670
Be careful not to tilt it.

270
00:14:17,000 --> 00:14:17,960
Align both sides.

271
00:14:18,360 --> 00:14:19,240
Don't scratch it.

272
00:14:19,510 --> 00:14:20,790
It was just pasted on.

273
00:14:21,600 --> 00:14:22,440
Let me see.

274
00:14:23,790 --> 00:14:24,630
Isn't it pretty?

275
00:14:25,480 --> 00:14:26,600
Not luxurious enough.

276
00:14:28,030 --> 00:14:28,870
Try this one.

277
00:14:29,630 --> 00:14:30,510
The pearl hairpin.

278
00:14:34,790 --> 00:14:35,630
Let me see.

279
00:14:35,840 --> 00:14:36,960
- It's nice.
- Looks pretty.

280
00:14:38,670 --> 00:14:39,510
No,

281
00:14:39,870 --> 00:14:40,790
I'm not satisfied.

282
00:14:41,150 --> 00:14:42,630
Take it down. Let's try the next set.

283
00:14:50,900 --> 00:14:56,660
(Joy)

284
00:15:09,630 --> 00:15:10,720
If the work is done, you can

285
00:15:10,870 --> 00:15:11,710
leave for a rest.

286
00:15:22,440 --> 00:15:23,280
It's strange.

287
00:15:23,840 --> 00:15:25,550
You are the one having the wedding.

288
00:15:26,480 --> 00:15:28,270
Why am I so nervous?

289
00:15:31,390 --> 00:15:33,240
Aren't you nervous at all?

290
00:15:35,720 --> 00:15:36,560
Not at all.

291
00:15:37,390 --> 00:15:38,270
Why should I be?

292
00:15:39,870 --> 00:15:40,750
